92
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,650
Go to the cave in West Mountain.

93
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:32,760
Hurry!

94
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:45,960
Benefactor.

95
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:46,760
General He.

96
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,040
General He.

97
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:56,820
Junior sister.

98
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,840
Why are you here?

99
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:01,400
General He.

100
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,600
I am Yun'er.

101
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,960
The daughter of Si Tu Wan Nan.

102
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:07,620
Junior sister.

103
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:10,040
I've let you down.

104
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:13,280
I couldn't stop Yun'er.

105
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:19,050
It's I who have let you down.

106
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:22,420
General He.

107
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:23,680
I've brought the paperweight.

108
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,480
Hong Guo said.

109
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:27,450
Do you have a way to counter this Soul-Crushing Palm?

110
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:32,480
We should act without delay.

111
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,680
Let's try it quickly.

112
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,360
What's wrong?

113
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,280
The paperweight you brought

114
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,600
