115
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:09,970
That's impossible.

116
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:13,530
This paperweight was given to me by Feng Chen.

117
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:15,500
Could it be that

118
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,690
he has been deceiving me all along?

119
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:23,400
Feng Chen is a man of deep schemes.

120
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:26,940
He's also obsessed with power plays.

121
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:31,160
His eagerness to pin the Blue Ghost's crimes on me this time

122
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:35,760
is certainly not as simple as avenging his father.

123
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,360
From now on,

124
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,600
stay away from him.

125
